metadata.name: Nouns Almanac Subscription
metadata.description:
The Nouns Almanac Subscription is an extremely limited edition of hand-crafted books. 

The Nouns Almanac Subscription includes a total of four reference books:

Series One: Nouns 0 - 256  
Series Two: Nouns 257 - 512  
Series Three: Nouns 513 - 768  
Series Four: Nouns 769 - 1024  
 
Each book is a beautifully designed reference guide that documents the unfolding story of Nouns. One page per Noun.

At the completion of the subscription, you will have received a total of 4 Noun Almanacs featuring a whopping 1,024 Nouns.
